NEW JERSEY DIVISION OF CHILD PROTECTION and Permanency, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
S.N., Defendant-petitioner,
and
H.M., Defendant. In the Matter of U.N., a Minor-Respondent. C-587 September Term 2017
080006 Supreme Court of New Jersey. February 9, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000409-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
